r. And we need to cut our cleaning cloth accordingly. If you are expecting to be maintaining your house to the same standard as when you've got more time and more energy, you're going to wear yourself out. This is maintenance season. All the good work that we've been putting in so far this year is going to stand you in really good stead. So we're just going to dip into that reserve a little bit, all of that contingency that we've built in, and we're just going to do one off over the summer to maintain, not stop altogether so that we move backwards, maintain the status quo. September, that's when the routines and the deep cleans and all of the good stuff start. We are in maintenance season.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 13362, "likes": 101, "comments": 3}], "still_climbing": false, "hook_type": "Problem", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "Da5OX92tWb1", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Da5OX92tWb1/", "caption": "And it\u2019s FREE \ud83d\ude1c", "timestamp": "2026-07-17T12:34:23.000Z", "videoDuration": 31.439, "videoPlayCount": 23749, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 3, "commentsCount": 4, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.flnk2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/750403006_18447993145142472_7537004355467627545_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.flnk2-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFEL2r9iKIrjjWKR0AuvAGmcoeIKugNgO2NNUzswQM-mwf0cAqsTLTOA8DQU0yDnMg&_nc_ohc=Lw9fitTx47EQ7kNvwGt7oM8&_nc_gid=eaxscA5yaG3mS07GzNElwA&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQCM-rpN3qht7_2ks7fMHYABWYWph3mHv5A8D3yr2z1l8A&oe=6A61D176&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQNluJKTp8wqjTYq0j32Bv38ZuNdgOGwN4TwUUK4jEH0FVtWk0w-zsHvWmOBm1a3VzeQfOvuwJMcKIzb5RYmXBxSzTB8fj1KNkGrnVo.mp4?_nc_cat=110&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=Mvfe9ZGTsc8Q7kNvwHzUFLs&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MjIwODY4NjQwNjU2MzIzMCwi