x/", "caption": "50% untethered \ud83d\ude02", "timestamp": "2026-07-15T09:04:24.000Z", "videoDuration": 50.153, "videoPlayCount": 19410, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 3, "commentsCount": 12, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/746842689_18447614110142472_3830629643603208483_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF8gESvhG-XVtFe6-wXM4jPYFa9Na9sQg5q4uHhVSWf6l_ihax62eBeslEqOVR291Q&_nc_ohc=74pAbaR0pP0Q7kNvwGocNbb&_nc_gid=8jZ2Ny-PWwRG0FE9Z4du8g&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDQ3NbvYlSGCMIdjVTbq8NswfW0DugkxQanMAFgkUGgSQ&oe=6A61C3D0&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQPrnxELyMPGAJlESmT3r9Y7zom-Kbw0QMqnU5sVuvzqIgtXovthoFofw-Ybd6uaiNjniIq4oMDtzO9Vp24_V1awCY5g14qw_SaWUMo.mp4?_nc_cat=106&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=4vt_7t00-gwQ7kNvwGnyOE0&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzIuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6NDQ1MTg0MDk5MTc2ODM2MCwiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjMsInZpX3VzZWNhc2VfaWQiOjEwMDk5LCJkdXJhdGlvbl9zIjo1MCwidXJsZ2VuX3NvdXJjZSI6Ind3dyJ9&ccb=17-1&vs=a9536a27968dca58&_nc_&_nc_gid=rE9oSZ3luqEP5ipS5rIZyQ&_nc_ss=72a8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQA7q5Eb_cK4iAJyOtuoiHEZpT7ZY9Z68IBve4h-xGrRmw&oe=6A5DF3BB", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27611593775162903"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM", "transcript": "I actually know who I need to talk to about this in real life too, but I know that you'll understand it. So Ben is at his end of year six, right? So he's my youngest. He's about to finish primary school, about to go into senior school. And today is my last ever day of double school. So Mike and I have shared school runs for years, like kind of like 50-50. I'll do two and a half days and he'll do another two and a half days. Today is my last day of living my life between 10 and two. And I genuinely don't know what to do because I have had this scaffold for 14 years. I have been doing school runs, I might be wrong, for 14 years. I have got to learn a whole new way of doing this. And I am 50% excited and 50% completely untethered.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 19358, "likes": 3, "comments": 12}], "still_climbing": false, "hook_type": "Personal Experience", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "Daw9QZpNZnU", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Daw9QZpNZnU/", "caption": "When that routine gets taken away it\u2019s normal to feel a bit all over the place \u2764\ufe0f", "timestamp": "2026-07-14T07:31:11.000Z", "videoDuration": 59.743, "videoPlayCount": 20151, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 130, "commentsCount": 9, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/746693526_1589791835813884_2244611729803289024_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEJbdytVLcKAg5mg7JjO7wxFCU_vvks6NLEfxsCZL8pE4Npd8fhy1huNCt-F7TGSP4&_nc_ohc=J1FUiZD_tS0Q7kNvwEsdzpl&_nc_gid=pndPKEVR54pHRdpS4lChDQ&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDu7G9G3-VF13ANFUukfRKV4UBYkoOt3t8C4rUGGSurmw&oe=6A61F0E9&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQNpjzg8q69GFoMiZnn_EJunuJZZyphkIFzZn2dVCxfPGJITCWmWNS2mcrnMoZKMk3evM1iIobcCYV2l3yA6bumAItcoSqeZgl6x_XI.mp4?_nc_cat=109&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=IqK_EgrhDuIQ7kNvwF8b7r8&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MjIyMTQ1OTY1MTk3OTQyMiwiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjQsInZpX3VzZWNhc2VfaWQiOjEwMDk5LCJkdXJhdGlvbl9zIjo1OSwidXJsZ2VuX3NvdXJjZSI6Ind3dyJ9&ccb=17-1&vs=87f8d0daa2aa52f2&_nc__JnyBxUCKAJDMywXQE3d0vGp--cYEmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MREAdf4HZeadAQA&_nc_gid=6X-Rm2J0C_7ztlEmqO6Z1g&_nc_ss=7c689&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQDeMzOQGpJjxFIhdBOv_AQUFOLS05VYeGmQXXFbcmVD_A&oe=6A5DE81E", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "37379677921623337"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM", "transcript": "Some, it's no surprise to you whatsoever that I love a routine. I don't have a routine, I can feel a little bit wibbly wobbly. I know that over the coming days some of you might be in the same boat, especially if you've got kids that are just about to break up for the summer. You might be thinking, hold on a minute, I've been looking forward to it, I've been looking forward to not having to do the school run. It might feel great when initially that routine relaxes, but there may come a point, not necessarily, but there may come a point where you're a bit more overwhelmed than you thought you were going to, and I'm going to tell you why. When you're doing the school run in the morning, you've got a hard deadline. You have got a framework imposed externally on you and you have not got a choice, which means that the decisions have kind of been taken out of your hands. When that school run doesn't exist for the summer, that framework doesn't exist either. All of a sudden you are having to make more decisions, and to an already overwhelmed brain, that doesn't feel great, and it can result in you feeling overloaded, a little bit snappy, not as relaxed as you thought you were going to do. Forewarned is forearmed. If you know that that wobble is coming, you're like, do you know what, this is entirely normal.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 20121, "likes": 130, "comments": 9}], "still_climbing": false, "hook_type": "Personal Experience", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "Daupk_qNOKT", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Daupk_qNOKT/", "caption": "Live NOW in The Organised Method app \u2728\ud83d\ude4c#cleaningroutine #cleaningmotivation", "timestamp": "2026-07-13T10:00:11.000Z", "videoDuration": 25.7, "videoPlayCount": 9526, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 76, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.fhnl3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/745314000_18447295009142472_4437777508389421562_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.fhnl3-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF4WlrcARzXeRK0uKd27zkfhjOA5UMBomldUdVFtSFNiBjUXbvDJGAs-RlP_GlvH8g&_nc_ohc=dy4MON29bocQ7kNvwFWswV3&_nc_gid=n0wN94tAm8PMwEijIUm_Kg&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQAC9l2mE00IqzIqTiQTEMzHRCBAI4F6NuXYP7hZq0GI9Q&oe=6A61ED53&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQPxJ286PTTEm46WuF4Uiz2etm1Kxu1Prgm8bpInyeWYzEwe-x8l-JdufM03OU9P-_2G2xwvBGWylY05y189IpRaQOJEzci_e5b9rFI.mp4?_nc_cat=108&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=gqBXYzTvkp8Q7kNvwGddvwK&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTc2MDg1NzYxNTA5MjQ4MiwiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjUsInZpX3VzZWNhc2VfaWQiOjEwMDk5LCJkdXJhdGlvbl9zIjoyNSwidXJsZ2VuX3NvdXJjZSI6Ind3dyJ9&ccb=17-1&vs=19228dd4bf3ff148&_nc_-gBhUCKAJDMywXQDmzMzMzMzMYEmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MREAdf4HZeadAQA&_nc_gid=1myS-0becjX89aDPOhVoRg&_nc_ss=7c689&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQC_NZnFepMr7G7SKd8f2XNOQ5W_2hcJUKmpU6778Pj46w&oe=6A5DFA4D", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "26925896313756154"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM", "transcript": "If you want to reset the engine rooms of your house this week, then you are in luck because one has just gone live. It's an hour session. We're going to divide our time between three rooms, the kitchen, the living room, and the bathroom. Rooms that get the most use consistently in your house. If you haven't got a lot of time, but you need an intentional, highly focused guided productivity session, then go and check it out now. I just know it's going to become a firm favorite over the summer, so make sure you bookmark it to get some clean done.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 9507, "likes": 76, "comments": 0}], "still_climbing": false, "hook_type": "Education", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "Dap0wXLN-9F", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Dap0wXLN-9F/", "caption": "Proactive cleaning for the win \ud83d\ude4c\u2728", "timestamp": "2026-07-11T13:01:47.000Z", "videoDuration": 38.8, "videoPlayCount": 40304, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 388, "commentsCount": 7, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-iad6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/741857443_18446954164142472_5256198507200380853_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-iad6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEt29sBPh73xwPDCWxiIe0NYJmj48_4ehS88jc23H4kBwW4NAkyEGWyUSHgQyD_Oj8&_nc_ohc=V7DuO-DSSC0Q7kNvwG1lXCY&_nc_gid=IiWYjxoLBZByx7EYjnleoQ&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQB7gZuez9Cvp6eYvLhaS9cgAyKhkw055yKrXc471ogEkg&oe=6A61DB43&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-dfw6-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQN2muscQ930aDsJfJyK8uAzJ2i52OkgIKXh7CR-TwA3OiQp3Hu7e-99uBwc3i1fVnAcb_wCtKSi5Uwyi_M4CEOU_rEuiSnxq084jAQ.mp4?_nc_cat=110&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-dfw6-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=PHHzq6X99b0Q7kNvwFaV4Kz&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6OTExMTU0MjE0NzE3ODU1LCJhc3NldF9hZ2VfZGF5cyI6NywidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjM4LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=1d0eaf1c6317e864&_nc_-pu70k6yeAxUCKAJDMywXQENmZmZmZmYYEmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MREAdf4HZeadAQA&_nc_gid=yftGO1_8vVIeof55c3uf9Q&_nc_ss=7ca8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQDa-PXpPog4UxMnE2mHuOzE1fZas-NtNC7tvVu-oBhXrQ&oe=6A5DE187", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "28704532339146713"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM", "transcript": "Can I tell you the most underrated strategy for keeping your house together? It's not a deep clean. It's not a full house reset. It's just doing the small stuff before it becomes a problem. I know that sounds stupidly simple. So things like making the bed before you go downstairs in the morning, not leaving the dishes to soak, it almost feels like it shouldn't be the answer, but it actually is. The mess is always going to come back because that is just what happens when people live in houses. It's not about having the perfect aesthetic, having a home that you feel like you can truly relax in. And we do that by staying one step ahead.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 40271, "likes": 388, "comments": 7}], "still_climbing": false, "hook_type": "Contrarian", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "Dam0D_1N1lg", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Dam0D_1N1lg/", "caption": "Looking for help solving the root cause and not just the symptoms? That\u2019s why I\u2019m here \ud83d\ude0d\ud83d\udc85\ud83c\udffb", "timestamp": "2026-07-10T08:58:23.000Z", "videoDuration": 35.966, "videoPlayCount": 23615, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 3, "commentsCount": 7, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/744537804_18446739643142472_1927869818625277497_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEVj-uV0itA00QTd_gsGgqDsEThM2OaaciD2TWo-Tq4k9cWuIkkY0EZ5u59cTWD9cM&_nc_ohc=TLPI4qTBzpcQ7kNvwH604pE&_nc_gid=d_gP-eg9yLq5hTgEFFWo-w&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDPR3y9reXDPR6oWVPvYU_awdjjQnEyHa7k5MPu0Vr7YA&oe=6A61D5A5&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-det1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQO3L_ujD9Dbd7ZI2m4zLl2sacVohB13scmZFFGuDAXiUkNVdMUiiJ-CYD4TqwnSHBsg928d4x26Taq_0y1Da9pwhKi0